title: France Banks Balance Sheet
description: Banks Balance Sheet in France increased to 11874324 EUR Million in September from 11857005 EUR Million in August of 2022. Banks Balance Sheet in France averaged 7070252.28 EUR Million from 1997 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 11874324 EUR Million in September of 2022 and a record low of 3147124 EUR Million in September of 1997. This page provides the latest reported value for - France Banks Balance Sheet - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
